  p.text_block #[a( href="https://twitter.com/antiflasher" ) Anton Lovchikov] created a logo that subtly references a #[a( href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qd8zT1YAUck" ) circular writing system] from the #[a( href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arrival_(film)" ) Arrival] movie

  h2 Font
  p.text_block We are using the free #[a( href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/35526923/KURBANISTIKA-free-font" ) Kurbanistika] font by Misha Priemyshev.
  p.text_block This is decorative font without focusing on readability. It should be used only for big and non-critical texts.

